Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteMimCap(25.10)                                        deleteMimCap(25.10)

Name
       deleteMimCap  - Deletes the mim caps from the design based on cell type
       or prefix

Syntax
       deleteMimCap

       [-help]

       [{[-cell <cellName>] [-prefix <prefixName>]} [-area llx lly urx ury]]

       Deletes the mim caps from the design based on cell type or prefix. This
       command can be used after addMimCap.

Parameters
       -area llx lly urx ury
              Deletes only the Mim caps that are in  the  specified  box.  The
              -cell or -prefix options are required when this option is speci-
              fied.

       -cell <cellType>
              Deletes the mim caps by cell type.

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each deleteMimCap parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man deleteMimCap.

       -prefix <prefixName>
              Deletes the mim caps by prefix.

Examples
              * The following command deletes the mim cap cell mim_cell1:

                deleteMimCap -cell mim_cell1

Related Information
              * addMimCap

